# secrets — the repo is public; see docs/WORKFLOW.md §9
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/application-local.yml
*.pem
**/secrets/
# unanchored on purpose: a `terraform apply` run from any directory must not be
# able to drop an un-ignored state file into a public repo
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
**/.terraform/
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
!**/.terraform.lock.hcl

